DESCRIPTION:Family Bike Ride & Ice Cream Social. Join Trinity Bikes for a c
 asual community bike ride around Redmond to celebrate Independence Day week
 . Meet at 5:30 PM\, ride starts at 6:00 PM. Easy 4-5 mile ride around town.
  Open to all ages and abilities. Helmets required. After the ride\, enjoy i
 ce cream sandwiches at the shop. Please RSVP. Good people. Good bikes. Good
  times.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260630T203042Z
LOCATION:Trinity Bikes\, 1730 SW Parkway Drive\, Redmond\, OR 97756
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:The Red\, White and Ride!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
